    "Title": "RESOURCE DRIVE: LARGE SHIP UNDER ATTACK",
    "Description": "This one is urgent. A transport ship of ours is currently under attack. They were able to share their last known location of <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> shortly before losing contact.\n\nSince this is a high-risk situation, <EM4>we strongly suggest you bring backup</EM4>. I have every confidence that you and your crew will be able to <EM4>occupy the outlaws long enough for the ship to complete repairs and escape with its cargo</EM4>.\n\nOutside of the contract\u2019s payment, you\u2019ll receive credit for the resources they deliver.\n\nLooking forward to hearing of your success.\n\n\nAster Remmington\nContractor Liaison Officer\nmicroTech",
